# Design Patterns

<!-- exodia:section:intro -->
> **Progressive disclosure:** this file holds short guardrails only (do/don't, 2-3 lines per topic). Detailed explanations live in `./docs/`. Drafted sections cite files and link to deep dives when a topic warrants more than ~3 lines.

<!-- exodia:section:body -->
{{MODEL_DRAFTS_SECTIONS_FROM_SCAN: one `##` section per repo-specific concern (components, modals, composables, imports, API, auth, tracking, testing, icons, accessibility, i18n, etc., as evidence supports). 2-3 lines of guardrails per section. When a topic needs more depth, spin out `./docs/<slug>.md` and replace the body of the section with a single line `See [docs/<slug>.md](docs/<slug>.md) for full details.` Cite files inline. No marketing prose.}}

